data.name: Label18.ToolTip
data.value: Start AppWatcher even if Home is not running. The AppWatcher is an internal process that detects game and app launches. Without the AppWatcher running OTT will not detect any game launches and Profiles will not work. The AppWatcher is automatically started when Oculus Tray Tool detects that Oculus Home is running, so you can most likely leave this box unchecked.
